  "description": "<p><strong> 6 Months Contract Pharmacy Assistant (Marine Parade)</strong><br /><strong>Salary:</strong> Up to <strong>$2,000 fixed</strong><br /><strong>Work Arrangement:</strong> 5.5 days, office hours (44 hours/week)</p><ul><li><p>Mon–Fri: 8:00am–5:00pm or 8:30am–5:30pm</p></li><li><p>Sat: 8:00am–12:00pm or 8:30am–12:30pm</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong><br />• Perform picking/packing of medications under Bin Coding System<br />• Support Medication Delivery Services (MDS), PILBOX, EZYBOX for remote medication collection<br />• Assist in patient management for Scriptless Dispensing workflows<br /><br />Interested candidates, do submit your resume to: jocelynchan@recruitexpress.com.sg OR telegram @jocelynchan</p><p>Jocelyn Chan| Consultant | Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)<br />Company EA Licence number : 99C4599<br />Personnel EA License: R1331820</p>",
